@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+# Pruned
+
+- A `--search`/`--contains` flag instead of a positional arg. Rejected: a single
+  positional term is the minimal interface; a flag adds no observable capability.
+- Case-insensitive / regex / field-selector / limit options. Rejected: not in the
+  acceptance criteria; substring `in` match is sufficient.
+- Filtering inside `store.load`. Rejected: would change the store's contract for
+  every caller; the filter is presentation-only and belongs in `cmd_list`.
diff --git a/.slime/corridor.md b/.slime/corridor.md
new file mode 100644
