@@ -0,0 +1,15 @@
+# Corridor: list-search
+
+Add an optional search term to `list` that shows only notes whose text contains it.
+
+## Goal Frontier
+- `list <term>` prints only notes whose `text` contains `<term>` (substring match).
+- `list` with no term keeps current behaviour (prints all notes, insertion order).
+
+## Start Frontier
+- `cli_notes/cli.py::cmd_list` — iterates `store.load(args.store)` and prints each note.
+- `cli_notes/cli.py::build_parser` — defines the `list` subparser.
+- `cli_notes/store.py::load` — returns the notes list; unchanged (filtering is a CLI concern).
+
+## Paths
+- cli_notes/cli.py
